6000|$|... "This is {{the last}} Will and Testament of me, Noel Vanstone, now living at Baliol Cottage, near Dumfries. I revoke, {{absolutely}} and in every particular, my former will executed on the thirtieth of September, eighteen hundred and forty-seven; and I hereby appoint Rear-Admiral Arthur Everard Bartram, of St. Crux-in-the-Marsh, Essex, <b>sole</b> <b>executor</b> of this my will." ...|$|E
